<h1 style="text-align: center;text-transform: uppercase;">Jobseeker</h1>
<div  style="margin-top: 30px;margin-left: 10px;font-family: 'Bitter', serif;font-size: 20px;">
    <div style="padding: 10px 10px 10px ;border-radius: 0px;" class="bg-drtail overflow-hidden">
    
